item.title: Holiday Etiquette Counts
item.description: Hey. Yeah so im kind of really free this season without true obligations (yay) , BUT etiquette should really be part of your character. Tact and Decorum will get you far. For Reals. Then a little on the new timeline of forgiveness which im loving btw. Maybe delulu a little. Idgaf.
